<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/848413-i-don-t-think-that-a-history-book-this">I don&#39;t think that a history book this condescending could be written anytime after about 1985.

That said, do people recommend moving on past the slightly uncomfortable first chapter?</a>
</div>
